name: VineTime
description: This is a ONE ROOM DOOM deathmatch level. You won't be guessing where anyone is: they're in the room you're in. There are lots of spots where you can remain hidden for short periods. However, I did a non-transitive layout on this level, so every ambush site can be ambushed in turn. (Watch for the famous Linden Slide-O-Death if you're killed against the wall on the upper level.)
